title.narrative: NUTRITION:HEALTH, NUTRITION AND Early Child Development (ECD) SYSTEMS

description.narrative: Health and school systems have enhanced capacities to prevent child and adolescent malnutrition, including obesity., which contributes to Adolescent Health And Nutrition, Prevention Of Stunting And Other Forms Of Malnutrition, Treatment Of Severe Acute Malnutrition. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2025, children benefit from quality, evidence-based and integrated health, nutrition and early childhood development systems
